(82, 39, 'Lobulo Frontal Material', '<h3>Lobulo Frontal Material.</h3><p><strong>Cara&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Surcos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Giros&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A.Funcionales&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Lateral Externa&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; *Surco frontal superior&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;*Giro Frontal Sup<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;*Surco frontal inferior&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; *Giro Frontal Medio<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;*Surco precentral&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;*Giro Frontal Inf<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- P.orbitaria<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- P.Triangular -&gt;Corresponde al area de broca<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- P.Opercular -&gt; Cubre parte de la insula<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; *Giro Precentral -&gt; Area motora principal&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Medial</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Inferior</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', 0),
(83, 39, 'Actividades', '<h3>Actividades</h3><p>Nombrar el recorrido de los surcos y los giros junto con su funcionalidad y su respectiva irrigacion</p>', '', '', 100),
(84, 45, 'IntroducciÃ³n a la NeurologÃ­a', '<h3>Introduccion a la Neurologia&nbsp;</h3><p>La neurologia es el amplio campo del estudio clinico del Sistema Nervioso.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Diagnostico</strong></p><p>* Los progresos terapeuticos a menudo preceden a la comprension basica de la enfermedad.&nbsp;</p><p>* Conocimiento teorico + Experiencia + Observacion + Pensamiento ordenado.&nbsp;</p><p>* Clave #1 para triunfar en la neurologia(como en toda especialidad) = Habiliad y fluidez en el metodo clinico.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Obtencion de signos y sintomas&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Interpretacion antofisiologica&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Diagnostico Sindromico&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Diagnostico Paologico y Diagnostico etiologico&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Diagnostico funcional - Pronostico.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Terapeutica c:</p><p>* Claro el metodo clinico puede y debe ser modificado segun si la situacion lo requiere.&nbsp;</p><p>* Los sintomas pueden ser malinterpretados. Por lo tanto es muy valido revisar 2 veces esa interpretacion sintomatica.</p><p>* Tambien es valido realizar repetidas exploraciones en caso de un diagnostico dificil.&nbsp;</p><p><em>* Social - El diagnostico exacto puede actuar como un elemento terapeutico.&nbsp;</em></p><p>* Los cuadros comunes aparecen comunmente.</p><p><strong>Categorias principales de enfermedades neurologicas&nbsp;<br />*&nbsp;</strong>Infecciosa<br />* Genetica - Congenita&nbsp;<br />* Traumatica&nbsp;<br />* Degenerativa&nbsp;<br />* Vascular&nbsp;<br />* Toxica&nbsp;<br />* Metabolica&nbsp;<br />* Neoplasica&nbsp;<br />* Inflamatoria - Inmunitaria&nbsp;<br />* Psicogena&nbsp;<br />* Yatrogenica&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Consejos Interrogatorio Clinico</strong></p><p>* Conseguir confianza del paciente.Hacer notar de la importancia del interrogatorio para que coopere.<br />* Notas al momento<br />* Verificar lo que el paciente relata de algun modo.&nbsp;<br />* Nunca sugerir el sintoma que el medico busca.&nbsp;<br />* Pedir al paciente que describa de la mejor manera lo que siente<br />* Se puede guiar de cierta manera.&nbsp;<br />* Evaluar como debuto la enferdad, como fue evolucionando, Como aparecieron y progresaron cada sintoma.&nbsp;<br />* Tener en cuenta el estado cognitivo del paciente.&nbsp;</p>', '', '', 0),
(85, 46, 'IntroducciÃ³n a los trastornos de la motilidad', '<h3>Introducci&oacute;n a los trastornos de la motilidad.</h3><p>* La mayor parte del sistema nervioso esta programada para el control de la funcon motora.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Fibrilacion</strong><br />* Explicacion probable: Incapacidad de la fibra aislada para mantener un potencial de membrana estable.<br />* No produce movimiento visible.&nbsp;<br />* Se registra con un EMG</p><p><strong>Fasciculacion</strong><br /><strong>*&nbsp;</strong>Sucede cuando una motoneurona se degenera.<br />* Axon inestable, genera impulsos -&gt; Potencial de accion muscular espontaneo de gran tama&ntilde;o.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Miocimia</strong><br />* Contracciones simultaneas o secuenciales de multiples unidades motoras. Mas relacionado con espasmos.&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"marker\">Actividad - Trastornos por segmentos medulares y por nervios.</span></p>', '', '', 0),
(86, 47, 'Degeneracion Paraneoplasica Cerebelosa', '<h3>Degeneracion Paraneoplasica Cerebelosa</h3><p>http://www.elsevier.es/es-revista-revista-senologia-patologia-mamaria-131-articulo-degeneracion-cerebelosa-paraneoplasica-como-presentacion-S0214158212000047</p>', '', '', 0),
