(7, 54, '<h3>Hemisferios Cerebrales</h3><p><strong>Forma:&nbsp;</strong>ovoide eje anteroposterior. Extremo posterior mas ancho.&nbsp;</p><p>*Separados por la fisura longitudinal.&nbsp;</p><p>*Separados del mesencefalo por <em>fisura transversa longitudinal.</em></p><p><em>*</em>Hasta el tercer mes de vida el cerebro es liso.&nbsp;</p><p>*Presencia de 3 caras</p><p>*Presencia de Surcos y Circonvoluciones primarias y secundarias</p><p>*Dividido en 6 lobulos.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Cara superolateral - Externa.&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* Sobre la cara interna de la calvaria&nbsp;</p><p>* Presencia del surco central, surco lateral y surco parietooccipital.&nbsp;</p><p>* Presencia de lobulos: Frontal, Parietal, Occipital y temporal.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>Surco central:&nbsp;</strong>Limite entre lobulo frontal y parietal.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Entre los giros precentral y poscentral.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Surco lateral:&nbsp;</strong>Limite entre lobulo frontal y parietal con el lobulo temporal.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cara anteroinferior -&gt; lateral -&gt; cara externa -&gt; Ramos anterior, ascendente, posterior -&gt; termina en giro&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; supramarginal&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Surco parietoccipital:&nbsp;</strong>Limite lobulo occipital y labulo parietal.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;Cara externa: Solo la porcion terminal.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Escotadura preocciptal:&nbsp;</strong>Limite entre lobulo temporal y occipital.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Cara Medial - Intermedio</strong></p><p>*Plana<br />*Estructurada alrededor del cuerpo calloso.<br />*Borde superior de convexidad superior<br />*Borde inferior interrumpido</p><p>*Bordes&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Surco del cuerpo calloso<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Surco del cingulo(callosomarginal)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;Posee una prolongacion &quot;ramo marginal&quot; que despues pasa a ser parte del surco&nbsp;subparietal&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Surco parietoccipital<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Surco central&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Surco colateral.<br />* Hay muchos otros surcos&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>lm</p>', '', '', '2018-05-31 00:41:22'),
