sp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Zona lateral -&gt;&nbsp;NMI&nbsp;de la musculatura de las extremidades.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;-&gt; Flexores mas al centro<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;-&gt; Extensores mas lateralmente.&nbsp;<br />wax * Lamina X -&gt; Parte central de la medula.</p><p><strong>Sustancia Blanca</strong><br />* Presencia de cordones dorsal, ventral y lateral.&nbsp;<br />* Presencia de tractos.&nbsp;<br />wax * En las regiones cervical y toracica superior el cordon dorsal se divide en el fasciculo gracil y cuneiforme.&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '2018-06-04 16:19:40');
